bsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor%27s_degrees">Bachelor&#39;s degrees</a>, 19<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Master%27s_degrees">Master&#39;s degrees</a>, one&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctoral_degree">Doctoral degree</a>&nbsp;(<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctor_of_Education">Doctor of Education</a>), and 11&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teaching_credential">teaching credentials</a>.</p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
