 in<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Montrose,_Colorado">Montrose, Colorado</a>. Colorado Mesa University grants two-year associate degrees, four-year bachelor&#39;s degrees, and master&#39;s degrees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Previously called Mesa State College (MSC), the school attained university status in August 2011, changing its name to Colorado Mesa University.</p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
