edu/harrisburg-university-of-science-and-technology-34659 ', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=harrisburg+university+ ', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=harrisburg+university+ ', '', '', '[""]', '["Harrisburg University has 7 undergraduate\\u00a0and 5\\u00a0Graduate school graduate\\u00a0programs in science and technology related disciplines. The university follows a trimester system. The University partners with many local\\u00a0civic organizations\\u00a0for student clubs and activities, such as the\\u00a0Harrisburg Young Professionals\\u00a0(HYP). HU students receive free membership in the organization,[6]\\u00a0which involves students in various community programs"]', '<p>Harrisburg University has 7 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Undergraduate">undergraduate</a>&nbsp;and 5&nbsp;<a href="http://harrisburgu.edu/graduate-students/">Graduate school graduate</a>&nbsp;programs in science and technology related disciplines. The university follows a trimester system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The University partners with many local&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Civil_society">civic organizations</a>&nbsp;for student clubs and activities, such as the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Harrisburg_Young_Professionals&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1">Harrisburg Young Professionals</a>&nbsp;(HYP). HU students receive free membership in the organization,<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harrisburg_University_of_Science_and_Technology#cite_note-6">[6]</a>&nbsp;which involves students in various community programs</p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47, 'Herguan university', 2008, 'USA', '', '', '595 Lawrence Expy, Sunnyvale, CA 94085, United States 2008', '595 Lawrence Expy, Sunnyvale, CA 94085, United States 2008', '', 'English Proficiency requirements \r\nTOEFL-79IBT \r\nIELTS-6.5\r\nThe following are the application deadlines for upcoming terms: \r\nSpring 2016 - October 11, 2015\r\nSummer 2016 - February 16, 2016\r\nFall 2016 - May 22, 2016\r\nTuition Fees\r\nPer credit $350\r\n\r\nCurricular Practical Training\r\nCPT will be processed in 7 business days from the date of application.\r\nCPT is employment that is required for your major or is for internship course credit. Examples: internships, and cooperative education.\r\nStudents must have maintained F-1 status for one academic year.\r\nPart-time CPT is 20 hours a week or less. If done during the school year, students must maintain full time status. It has no effect on OPT.\r\nFull-time CPT is more than 40 hours a week. If you\r\n do more than 12 months of full-time CPT, you lose your OPT option.\r\nCPT fees are not refundable.', 'public', '', 'Master of Science in Computer Science (MSCS Masters in Business Administration (MBA):  Admission requirements English Proficiency requirements  TOEFL-79IBT  IELTS-6.5 The following are the application deadlines for upcoming terms:  Spring 2016 - October 11, 2015 Summer 2016 - February 16, 2016 Fall 2016 - May 22, 2016 Tuition Fees Per credit $350  Curricular Practical Training CPT will be processed in 7 business days from the date of application. CPT is employment that is required for your major or is for internship course credit. Examples: internships, and cooperative education. Students must have maintained F-1 status for one academic year. Part-time CPT is 20 hours a week or less. If done during the school year, students must maintain full time status. It has no effect on OPT. Full-time CPT is more than 40 hours a week. If you  do more than 12 months of full-time CPT, you lose your OPT option. CPT fees are not refundable.  Herguan University  Herguan University campus Type Private Established 2008 President Dr. Ying Qiu Wang Location Sunnyvale, California, United States 37.38648°N 121.99691°WCoordinates: 37.38648°N 121.99691°W Nickname Estimated Cost of living: Tuition Fee: Application Fee: Type of Accommodation                                         Social Media Links: Videos Link: 	 Photos of Universities:     HGU $10,000 USD aprox per year  $350 per unit  Off campus & on campus  Linked in - https://www.linkedin.com/company/herguan-university ', 'Dr. Ying Qiu Wang', '', '', '', 'on', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/herguan-university ', '', '', '', '', '', '[""]', '["The University''s\\u00a0MBA, MSCS, and MSEE programs operate with approval from the California Department of Consumer Affairs''\\u00a0Bureau for Private Postsecondary Education. The Bureau is not an accreditation agency and does not confer accreditation status to educational institutions. On August 2, 2012,\\u00a0Immigration and Customs Enforcement\\u00a0(ICE) served Herguan with a notice of intent to withdraw its SEVP certification.\\u00a0Herguan''s CEO has been indicted on visa fraud charges.  On September 18, 2012, ICE revoked Herguan''s SEVP approval, but rescinded that decision a day later.\\u00a0According to ICE, Herguan''s lawyer had sent the response to a wrong email address. The San Jose Mercury News reported on evidence that Herguan officials tried to get help from local and state politicians regarding the ICE investigation.  On April 9, 2015, Herguan''s former CEO, Jerry Wang, pleaded guilty to visa fraud.\\u00a0On April 10, 2015, ICE moved to revoke Herguan''s SEVP approval.  On September 14, 2015, Herguan''s former CEO, Jerry Wang, was sentenced to 12 months in prison and forfeiture of $700K for his role in a student visa fraud scheme at Herguan."]', '<p>The University&#39;s&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MBA">MBA</a>, MSCS, and MSEE programs operate with approval from the California Department of Consumer Affairs&#39;&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/California_Bureau_for_Private_Postsecondary_Education">Bureau for Private Postsecondary Education</a>. The Bureau is not an accreditation agency and does not confer accreditation status to educational institutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On August 2, 2012,&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immigration_and_Customs_Enforcement">Immigration and Customs Enforcement</a>&nbsp;(ICE) served Herguan with a notice of intent to withdraw its SEVP certification.&nbsp;Herguan&#39;s CEO has been indicted on visa fraud charges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On September 18, 2012, ICE revoked Herguan&#39;s SEVP approval, but rescinded that decision a day later.&nbsp;According to ICE, Herguan&#39;s lawyer had sent the response to a wrong email address. The San Jose Mercury News reported on evidence that Herguan officials tried to get help from local and state politicians regarding the ICE investigation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On April 9, 2015, Herguan&#39;s former CEO, Jerry Wang, pleaded guilty to visa fraud.&nbsp;On April 10, 2015, ICE moved to revoke Herguan&#39;s SEVP approval.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On September 14, 2015, Herguan&#39;s former CEO, Jerry Wang, was sentenced to 12 months in prison and forfeiture of $700K for his role in a student visa fraud scheme at Herguan.</p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48, 'Humboldt State University', 1913, 'USA', '', '', '1 Harpst St, Arcata, CA 95521, United States', '1 Harpst St, Arcata, CA 95521, United States', '', '\r\nxUPLOAD A SCANNED PDF OF EACH OFFICIAL TEST SCORE REPORT TO THE STUDENT''S RECORD IN WELLSPRING AMS.\r\nxWHEN PDFS OF DOCUMENTS ARE PROVIDED ON A STUDENT''S APPLICATION, THE SCHOOL WILL REQUIRE THAT THE STUDENTS PROVIDE ORIGINAL COPIES UPON ARRIVAL ON CAMPUS. PLEASE MAKE SURE THAT THE STUDENT HAS THESE DOCUMENTS IN THEIR POSSESSION WHEN THEY BOARD THEIR FLIGHT TO THE UNITED STATES.\r\n1. High School Transcript\r\npdf\r\nScan all high school diplomas, exams and/or transcripts. Upload the scan as a PDF to AMS.\r\n2. College Transcript\r\nTransfer Only\r\nPDF Original Upon Arrival\r\nScan all college or university records. Upload the scan as a PDF to AMS.\r\n3. Financial Statement\r\nProvide a pdf of an affidavit of financial support and a supporting financial document. If you do not have a standard format for an affidavit and supporting financial document, you may use the general format below.\r\nDOWNLOAD FINANCIAL AFFIDAVIT FORM\r\nUpload a PDF to Wellspring AMS\r\n4. Personal Statement\r\nNo\r\nUpload a PDF to Wellspring AMS\r\n5. Passport\r\nPlease provide a scanned copy of photo page form the applicant''s passport\r\nProgram\r\nAnnual\r\nTuition\r\nDiscount\r\nBiology (MS)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nBusiness – Master of Business Administration (MBA) C\r\n$20,876\r\nNo\r\nEducation (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nEnglish (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nEnvironmental Systems (MS)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nKinesiology (MS)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nNatural Resources (MS)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPsychology- Academic Research- Biological Psychology (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPsychology- Academic Research- Developmental Psychopathology (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPsychology- Academic Research- Social & Environmental Psychology (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPsychology- Counseling (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPsychology- School Psychology (MA)\r\n$6,696\r\nNo\r\nPublic Socio