(60, 'Lincoln University', 1926, 'USA', '', '', 'Oakland, California, United States\r\n', 'Oakland, CA 94612 Contact No. 1-510-628-8010 Email: admissions@lincolnuca.edu\r\nAbout Lincoln University', '', '', 'public', '', 'Lincoln University confers the following degrees: Doctor of Business Administration (DBA) Master of Business Administration (MBA) Master of Science (MS) in International Business Master of Science (MS) in Finance Management Bachelor of Arts (BA) in Business Administration Bachelor of Science (BS) in Diagnostic Imaging   Intakes :  Fall/ Spring/ Summer    Tuition & Fees for International Students  Undergraduate Tuition & Fees :  http://www.lincolnuca.edu/admission/index#/admission/fees           Graduate Tuition & Fees : http://www.lincolnuca.edu/admission/index#/admission/fees       International Admission Requirements :   1. An "Applicant’s Declaration of Finances" form and a "Sponsor’s Affidavit of Support" form with a bank statement or a verification letter from an officer of the bank or other financial institution giving the present balance, which must equal or exceed the amount required for one year of study ($18,960). 2. Proof of English proficiency is required for all regular students from countries or schools where English is not an official educational language.  3. A photocopy of the passport or equivalent document. 4. All documents must be accompanied by notarized English translation. 5. APPLICATION FEE (non-refundable) $75 6. No GRE/GMAT required   For more information visit university website : Email: www.lincolnuca.edu   Prepared by  : Flavia Trindad ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------           Lincoln University Motto Learn More, Earn More, Much More! Type Private non-profit university Established 1926 President Mikhail Brodsky, Ph.D. Students 811 Location Oakland, California, United States Website Estimated Cost of living: Tuition Fee: Application Fee: Type of Accommo