 University provides traditional and accelerated programs of study that combine in-depth knowledge with hands-on clinical practice focused on professional education in&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmacy">pharmacy</a>and the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_science">health sciences</a>. Its location within the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Longwood_Medical_and_Academic_Area">Longwood Medical and Academic Area</a>&nbsp;provides students with academic and clinical opportunities at various prestigious medical and research institutions. Since 2000, MCPHS University has expanded to include two additional campuses, located in&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Worcester,_Massachusetts">Worcester, Massachusetts</a>, and&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manchester,_New_Hampshire">Manchester, New Hampshire</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
