(94, 'Flinders International University', 1966, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Flinders-International.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Flinders-International.jpg', 'Bedford Park, Adelaide, Australia', 'Sturt Drive, Bedford Park, Adelaide SA 5042, Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PUBLIC', '9000-10000 AUD', 'Arts and languages\nBusiness and commerce\nComputing and information technology\nCreative arts, media and design\nCulture, heritage, tourism and theology\nEducation\nEngineering\nEnvironment\nGovernment and policy\nInternational affairs\nHealth and medicine\nLaw and justice\nNursing and midwifery\nScience and mathematics\nSocial work and psychology\n Intensive English Language Institute (IELI) \n(conveniently located on campus at Flinders)\nEynesbury College\nSouth Australian College of English (SACE) - Adelaide and Melbourne campuses\nEnglish College of Adelaide', '', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 8 8201 3911', 'admission@studymetro.com', '$21,632 per course', 'spring/fall, summer', '100', 'https://www.facebook.com/FlindersUniversity/', 'www.flinders.edu.au/international-students/', 'https://twitter.com/flinders\n', 'https://plus.google.com/+flindersuniversity\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flinders-university\n', 'https://www.instagram.com/flindersuniversity/?hl=en', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/FlindersUniversity\n', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'Flinders International', 'Studying at Flinders University offers you an outstanding education in one of the world’s most liveable cities. Our courses combine academic excellence with industry experience, providing you with the skills you need to succeed in your career.\n\nFlinders is ranked in the top 300 universities worldwide and we have a vibrant community of international students from over 90 countries.', 'Find out about our courses and fees; learn about our rankings and reputation; and hear from our students about their experiences at Flinders.\n\nApplying to Flinders\n\nInformation about how to apply; including entry requirements, pathways, scholarships, finding an agent and more. Find out how to accept your offer.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(95, 'Gold Coast Learning Centre', 0, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Gold-Coast-Learning-Centre.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Gold-Coast-Learning-Centre-1.jpg', 'Surfers Paradise', '18-22 Orchid Ave, Surfers Paradise QLD 4217, Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PRIVATE', '9000-10000 AUD', 'Certificate II in Business (BSB20107)\nCertificate III in Business Administration (BSB30407)\nCertificate IV in Business (BSB40207)\nDiploma of Business (BSB50207)                           Certificate IV in Accounting                                          Diploma of Accounting                                           BAS Agent Short Course               Certificate IV in Leadership and Management                                               Diploma of Leadership and Management                                                            Diploma of MarketingAdvanced Diploma of Marketing                                                           Certificate IV in Training & Assessment   Certificate IV in Workplace Health and Safety                                                                          Diploma of Human Resources', '', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 7 5531 6788', 'admission@studymetro.com', '', 'spring/fall, summer', '100', 'www.goldcoaststudy.com/\n', 'https://www.facebook.com/GoldCoastLearningCentre/\n', 'https://twitter.com/gclcstudy\n', 'https://plus.google.com/+Goldcoaststudy4217/videos\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gold-coast-learning-centre', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/256734333/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTwwow_c-Xyv2UxSZ8hqgtA\n', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'Gold Coast Learning Centre', 'GCLC | English College is situated right in the heart of Surfers Paradise on the Gold Coast and features excellent facilities, quality teaching programs and dedicated, enthusiatic and experienced staff.\nLearn English at the Gold Coast''s finest English College while you settle in to Australia and enjoy the famous Surfers Paradise lifestyle of the Gold Coast, Australia''s world famous tourist destination.\nGCLC | English College offers a range of English language courses to suit all levels.\nLocated right in the heart of Surfers Paradise, GCLC | English College is surrounded by the fantastic shops, bustling nightlife and of course the famous Surfers Paradise beach.\nCareful supervision from the experienced, dedicated staff of Gold Coast Learning Centre ensures students can progress as fast as they want to.', 'The staff of GCLC | English College are dedicated to helping our students succeed in their English studies and enjoying their spare time in beautiful Surfers Paradise.\nOur teaching team is highly qualified and our friendly, experienced teachers are always willing to take the time to help students achieve success in their studies.\nExtra homework, worksheets and advice can easily be arranged for the hard-working student. Many of our staff have experience teaching English in other countries and understand the concerns of international students.\nAt GCLC | English College we help you develop your English language skills through communication with your fellow students and your teachers in useful, real-life situations.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
