(97, 'Macquarie Education Group Australia (MEGA)', 0, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Macquarie-Education-Group-Australia-MEGA.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Macquarie-Education-Group-Australia-MEGA-1.jpg', 'Sydney', '9/225 Clarence St, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PRIVATE', '9000-10000 AUD', 'General English\nIELTS Preparation\nEnglish for Academic Purposes\nFCE Preparation\nHigh School Preparation\nMEGA Vocational\nCertificate III to Advanced Diploma in Accounting\nCertificate IV to Advanced Diploma in Marketing', '', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 2 9299 6788', 'admission@studymetro.com', '', 'spring/fall, summer', '100', 'http://www.mega.edu.au/', 'https://www.facebook.com/macquarie.institute.sydney/', 'https://twitter.com/mega_sydney/status/735668747491368960', 'https://plus.google.com/109358669565910627130/about', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/macquarie-education-group-australia', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/269301227/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_R4GymtNFTA', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'MEGA', 'Students at MEGA benefit from our qualified team of teaching professionals with real-world, best-practice experience in industry and the global business arena, offering world-class standards in English Language, Accounting, Business and Marketing education.\n \nA MEGA education equips students with the English language and vocational skills, knowledge and exposure to current business practices and work experience needed to succeed in our competitive world.\n?\n', 'Programmes at MEGA are state-of-the-art, comprehensive and demanding, creating a solid foundation in business techniques, preparing young adults to shape the future of their chosen discipline.\n?\nWhatever age and ambitions, I am confident and convinced that MEGA can help our students to advance.\n?\nYour personal development and welfare are important to us. We look forward to meeting with each student, to discuss how we can complement your background and help you achieve your goals.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(98, 'S P Jain School of Global Management', 2004, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/S-P-Jain-School-of-Global-Management.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/S-P-Jain-School-of-Global-Management-1.jpg', 'Sydney', '5 Figtree Dr, Sydney NSW 2127, Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PRIVATE', '9000-10000 AUD', '.1 BBA (Bachelor of Business Administration)\n4.2 BBC (Bachelor of Business Communications)\n4.3 BEC (Bachelor of Economics)\n4.4 MGB (Master of Global Business)\n4.5 GMBA (Global Master of Business Administration)\n4.6 EMBA (Executive Master of Business Administration)\n4.7 Big Data & Analytics (Full Time OR Part Time)\n4.8 Executive Education\n4.9 Global FMB (Global Family Managed Business)\n4.10 Digital Marketing & Metrics (Full Time OR Part Time)\n4.11 Global Luxury Goods & Services Management (Full Time)', 'Nitish Jain', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 2 8970 6800', 'admission@studymetro.com', '$50,215/yr', 'spring/fall, summer', '100', 'www.spjain.edu.au/\n', 'https://www.facebook.com/spjainschoolofglobalmanagement/', 'https://twitter.com/spjainglobal', 'https://plus.google.com/+SpjainOrgglobal\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/s-p-jain-center-of-management\n', 'https://www.instagram.com/spjain_sydneycampus/\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tUFYhgl3dzE\n', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'S P Jain School of Global Management', 'S P Jain School of Global Management opened the Sydney campus in 2012.The campus is located in the Sydney Olympic Park business district, the campus is surrounded by exceptional facilities for sports and recreation. The campus has 12 auditorium style classrooms, breakout rooms, café with its own kitchen, lounges and other facilities expected at a premium business school campus. Students are provided their own space and serenity to study, and at the same time have an opportunity to get involved in the exciting culture of Sydney to experience the true essence of global learning.', 'Sydney, a truly global city, is rated among the world''s best cities for its combination of business, culture, sports, food and recreation. The city draws over 150,000 international students every year and is home to 48% of Australia''s top 100 companies. Sydney offers an exceptional environment not only for studying, but also for experiencing a dynamic and diverse city. ', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
