 Here students will enjoy the relaxed atmosphere of a premier tourist destination with easy access once again to accommodation, restaurants, food outlets, shops, sports stadium, learning facilities and library.\n\nBoth Campuses are easily accessible by public transport due to their prime locations.', 'As a nationally recognised RTO, Spencer College are fully committed to continuous improvement. Our uncompromising stance on “student integrity” has earned us the reputation that we currently enjoy. Spencer College takes pride in its ever expanding faculties of Business, Management, Tourism and Hospitality and are proud to offer our services to students from 10 different nationalities.\n\nSpencer College has excellent student support services. Our friendly staff values our students by ensuring their needs are met. Spencer College values its experienced and friendly staff.\n\nCourses are practical and functional, preparing individuals with a mix of well-rounded skills and knowledge to embark on an interesting career.\n\nSpencer College has grown every year since its inception and looks forward to future growth including higher education programs, a wider range of courses and the opening of new campuses.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
