(111, 'Acsenda School of Managment', NULL, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Acsenda_School_of_Management_Logo_2013.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ascenda-school-of-management.jpg', ' St, Vancouver,Canada', '1090 W Pender St, Vancouver, BC V6E 2N7, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL score of at least 550 (paper-based) or 80 iBT (internet based). The institution code is B118.\nIELTS score of at least 6.5 with no band less than 6.0\nCAEL – Band 60\nPearson (PTE – Academic) -58+\nMELAB – 80+\nCLB -8+\nCEFR – C1\nOR\nAcsenda School of Management’s English Placement Test (EPT) – 80 or above', 'Private', '$ CAD 10,000 approx', '• Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA)\n\n• Bachelor of Hospitality Management (BHM),\n• Post Graduate Certificate in General Management\n\n• Post Graduate Diploma in Human Resources Management\n\n• Post Graduate Diploma in International Business Management\n\n• Post Graduate Diploma in Marketing\n', 'Dr. Lindsay Redpath', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '+1 604-430-5111', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.acsenda.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Acsenda', 'https://twitter.com/acsenda', 'https://plus.google.com/+AcsendaSchoolofManagementVancouver', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/acsenda-school-of-management---vancouver', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-p9y2boePDAcpQWcjBXSgg', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Acsenda School of Management', 'Located in Vancouver on the Pacific Coast of Canada, Acsenda School of Management is a specialist business and leadership institute with a uniquely international focus. Acsenda is a small, private institution that offers undergraduate programs in the Province of British Columbia Canada with the Consent of the BC Minister of Advanced Education under the authority of British Columbia’s Degree Authorization Act after a rigorous review of the quality of its programs and organizational capability. Acsenda has been offering a Bachelor of Business Administration Degree (BBA) with multiple specialties since 2004 and expects to offer a Bachelor of Hospitality Management Degree (BHM) beginning in January 2015.', 'We emphasize a unique combination of small class sizes, open access to instructors and the use of the latest technology. We are able to get to know our students. We understand their strengths, and work with them directly to foster a deeper level of critical thinking and business knowledge.\nAs a truly international management and leadership school, our campus is filled with bright minds from around the world. As a result, our graduates don’t just get a business education—they get a broad, cross-cultural experience that prepares them for the reality of international business\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
