(130, 'Royal Roads University', 1995, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Royal-roads.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Royal-roads.jpg', ' Victoria,, Canada', '2005 Sooke Rd, Victoria, BC V9B 5Y2, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 90  IELTS 6.5  MELAB  85 CAEL  70', 'Private', '$ CAD 10,000 approx', 'Master of Business Administration in Executive Management\n\nMaster of Global Management\n\nGraduate Certificate in Advanced Coaching Practices\n\nGraduate Certificate in Change Management\n\nGraduate Certificate in Executive Coaching\n\nGraduate Certificate in Organization Design and Development\n\nGraduate Certificate in Workplace Innovation\n\nBachelor of Business Administration\n\nBachelor of Commerce in Entrepreneurial Management\n\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 800-788-8028', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.royalroads.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/royalroadsu', 'https://twitter.com/royalroads', 'https://plus.google.com/+RoyalRoadsUniversityVictoria', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/royal-roads-university-10800', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/228833813/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/RoyalRoadsUni', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Royal Roads University', 'Royal Roads University is a public university in Canada with a top-level reputation offering a quality education. There is a strong emphasis on a practical, applied programs delivered by award-winning faculty with real-world experience. Degree programs are developed in collaboration with industry experts and taught by local and internationally recognized professionals who are leading practitioners in their fields.', 'Why Royal Roads University?\nRoyal Roads University graduates leave with the skills employers want. Degree programs develop employment skills through applied research and a professional outcomes-based learning model. Work experience through internships is built into