rk Production Technician Apprenticeship\nPower Engineering\nPractical Nursing\nPractical Nursing Bridging\nPractical Nursing Refresher\nPrairie Horticulture\nSocial Service Worker\nSustainable Food Systems\nTaxidermy\nTESOL\nWelder (Continuing Studies)\nWelder Apprenticeship', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 204-725-8700', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://assiniboine.net/', 'https://www.facebook.com/accmanitoba/', 'https://twitter.com/accmb', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/assiniboine-community-college', 'https://www.instagram.com/accmb/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7VlzO6_r8s0ZiVVqmagLYQ', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Assiniboine Community College', 'ACC offers more than 40 diploma and certificate programs across a variety of disciplines including culinary arts and hospitality, business, agriculture and environment, health and human services, trades and technology. The college also delivers apprenticeship programming in a range of skilled trades disciplines, upgrading for post-secondary/adult education, English language training and continuing studies courses.', 'Why Assiniboine Community College?\nAssiniboine Community College (ACC) has been providing exceptional learning experiences for over 50 years. For staff and students alike, we offer unparalleled learning environments. Our college responds well to the demands and requirements of the Manitoba labour market. Instructors follow the philosophy of learn by doing, combining theory with hands-on learning inside classrooms, labs, kitchens, shops, fields and the college’s sustainable greenhouse. ACC is an accredited college with the Government of Manitoba Council on Post-Secondary Education.\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(143, 'Bishop''s University', 1843, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bishop-University.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bishop-University.jpg', 'Sherbrooke, Quebec, Canada', '2600 College Street Sherbrooke, Quebec, J1M 1Z7', NULL, 'TOEFL 90  IELTS 6.5  MELAB  85 CAEL  70', 'Public', '$CAD 11,000 approx', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 819-822-9600', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.ubishops.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ubishops', 'https://twitter.com/ubishops', 'https://plus.google.com/115278461007476822292', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/bishop''s-university-10888', 'https://www.instagram.com/ubishops/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/bishopsuniversity', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Bishop''s University', 'Located in the beautiful Eastern Townships region of the province of Quebec, Bishop’s is a unique English-language university that offers its students an undergraduate university experience like no other.\n\n', 'Why Bishop''s University\nOur students choose us because they want to challenge themselves: To learn. To be bold. To speak up and be heard. To become a leader. To make a difference.\nIs this you? If so, you’re in the right place.\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(144, 'Brescia university college ', 1919, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Brescia.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Brescia.jpg', ' London, Canada', '1285 Western Rd, London, ON N6G 1H2, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 83   IELTS 6.5', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'Undergraduate Programs\n1. Bachelor of Arts\n2. Bachelor of Management & Organizational Studies\n3. Bachelor of Science (Foods & Nutrition)\n4. Bachelor of Arts (Human Ecology)\n5. Bachelor of Science (Human Ecology)\nGraduate Programs \nMaster of Science in Foods and Nutrition (MScFN)\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 519-432-8353', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://brescia.uwo.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BresciaUniversityCollege', 'https://twitter.com/BresciaUC?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor', 'https://plus.google.com/+bresciauniversitycollege', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/brescia-university-college-10835', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/8528879/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/bresciauniversityc', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Brescia University College', 'Brescia is Canada’s only women’s university. We were founded in 1919 by the Ursuline Sisters, strong women of faith who are committed to social justice, community service, and the development of women. While our roots are in the Catholic faith, we are open to – and embrace – women of all faiths.\n\n\nBrescia is affiliated with Western University, the third-largest university in the province. That means you’ll benefit from the small, supportive atmosphere at Brescia while still enjoying the resources Western has to offer.\n', 'Why Brescia University College?\nAt Brescia, you’ll:\n\n\n• Have endless opportunities to enhance your leadership skills\n\n• Benefit from an exceptional education that is tailored to you and the way you learn best\n\n• Learn from compassionate professors who will mentor – and empower – you\n\n• Feel comfortable to openly share your opinions and ideas – in the classroom and beyond\n\n• Bond with women who share your desire to be truly educated and to make a difference in the world\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
