oors first opened. Brock’s story is about a community that rose up and built the institution it wanted for its future.', 'Why Brock University?\n\n\nWe nurture both sides of the brain\n\n\nOur unique philosophy takes students beyond the pursuit of academic excellence.\nBrock is a place where left-brain and right-brain thinking come together. Students develop rational/analytical thinking in concert with their emotional/creative sides. We view community involvement as crucial to developing intelligent, well-rounded members of society.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(146, 'Camber College', 2003, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/cambercollege_logo2.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/camber-college-1.jpg', 'Powell River, Canada', '4750 Joyce Ave, Powell River, BC V8A 2C3, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 90  IELTS 6.5  MELAB  85 CAEL  70', 'Private', '$ CAD 10,000 approx', 'Academic English Program    Intensive English    English Plus Program   Family Plus Program    Camber Summer Camps  Camber Winter Camps', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 604-485-5115', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://cambercollege.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/camberworld', 'https://twitter.com/cambercollege', 'https://plus.google.com/+CamberCollegePowellRiver', 'https://ca.linkedin.com/in/camber-college-3326a936', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/318039753/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/cambercollege', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Camber College', 'Camber College is one of Canada’s most innovative and dynamic language centers. Established in 2003, Camber College has been providing students with high quality English language training for 12 years.\n\n\n\nAt Camber College, we teach English in many different ways because we know that all students are unique, learn differently and have different goals. Our unique programs, both in and out of the classroom, maximize each student''s educational adventure\n', 'Why Camber College?\nThere are many different ways to learn English, but we strongly believe there''s no better way than learning face-to-face. We believe the best method is surrounding yourself with its native culture and people.\n\n\n\n• We have 12 years of experience teaching English and providing students with world-class language education.\n• We celebrate all cultures and learn from diversity. We find ways to communicate our cultural heritage. We are open minded, reflective and caring about all cultures. Innovative classes and friendly, family atmosphere.\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(147, 'Centennial College', 1966, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/logo-centennial.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Centennial-College.jpg', 'Toronto,  Canada', '941 Progress Ave, Toronto, ON M1K 5E9, Canada', NULL, 'IELTS (Academic) 6.5+ (with no single test score below 6.0*)\nPearson Test of English (Academic) 60+\nITEP ( International Test of English Proficiency) 4.1+', 'Public', '$ CAD 10,000 approx', 'http://www.centennialcollege.ca/programs-courses/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1416-289-5000', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.centennialcollege.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/centennialcollege', 'https://twitter.com/centennialEDU', 'https://plus.google.com/+CentennialCollegeToronto', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/centennial-college/', 'https://www.instagram.com/centennialcollege/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/CentennialCollegeON', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Centennial College', '.Centennial College is the first government-accredited college in Ontario, Canada.  Centennial has four campuses and eight specialized academic schools in Toronto, offering post-secondary, post-graduate and fast-track programs in Business, Engineering Technology and Applied Science, Communications, Media and Design, Health and Community studies, Hospitality, Tourism and Culture and Transportation as well as English Language Learning (ELL) and foundations programs for college and university preparation.\n', 'Why Centennial College?\n• #1 College Choice for International Students in Canada! \n• 2015 Canadian Bureau for International Education (CBIE) President''s Award for Distinguished Leadership in International Education \n• First place for Engineering students in the 2015 National Engineering Month!\n• First prize for Innovation in Applied Research in Canada (CICan 2015 Exellence Award)\n• Top honors at 2015 Canadian Public Relations Society Awards!\n• Ontario Community Newspaper Association (OCNA) 2015 award for Best College/University Newspaper Website!\n• First place in the Ontario Association for Applied Architectural Sciences (OAAAS) Student Awards\n• Leader in International Education with CBIE and CICan Internationalization Excellence Awards.\n\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(148, 'Conestoga College', NULL, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Conestoga_College_logo.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/conestoga.jpg', ' Doon Valley Dr, Kitchener, Canada', '299 Doon Valley Dr, Kitchener, ON N2G 4M4, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 90  IELTS 6.5  MELAB  85 CAEL  70', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'http://www.conestogac.on.ca/international/programs/program-list.jsp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 519-748-5220', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.conestogac.on.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConestogaCollege/', 'https://twitter.com/ConestogaC', 'https://plus.google.com/106254807073766679662', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/conestoga-college-institute-of-technology-and-advanced-learning', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/224955956/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/conestogapolytechnic', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Conestoga College', 'Conestoga is one of Canada''s leading polytechnic institutes, consistently ranked among the very best colleges in the province of Ontario for graduate employment as well as student, graduate and employer satisfaction. Our highly rated college provides international students with all of the skills and opportunities needed to gain professionally recognized credentials which can lead to exciting professions in Canada. At Conestoga, we provide many study levels including; English, Bachelor (Degree), Post-graduate, Diploma, and Graduate certificates. Even students with no minimum English requirement (IELTS or TOEFL), are able to pursue their higher education level with the conditions of completion of our English Program.', 'Why Conestoga College? \n1. Ontario''s fastest growing college, with enrolment growth of more than 42 per cent over the last five years\n2. Consistently ranked among the very best of Ontario''s colleges for graduate employment as well as student, graduate and employer satisfaction\n3. More than 120 full-time certificate, diploma, degree and post-graduate programs, many with co-op options\n4. You''re among friends with more than 1600 international students from 77 countries in an overall full-time student population of 11,000\n5. New educational facilities that provide state-of-the art training in a variety of in-demand fields\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
