(161, 'Interlangues Language School', 1976, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Interlangues-Language-School.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Interlangues-Language-School.jpg', 'Ottawa,  Canada', '444 Maclaren, Ottawa, ON K2P 0M8, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 90  IELTS 6.5  MELAB  85 CAEL  70', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'University/College Preparation\nInterlangues will fully prepare you for your post-secondary education. Whether it be Test Preparation, a particular skill focus, or subject specific vocabulary, we have the perfect program for you.\n\nInterlangues can help you prepare for all the major English tests such as:\nTOEFL\nTOEIC\nEAP (English for Academic Purposes)\nIELTS, etc.\n\nWe also offer focused training on particular language skills such as:\nPhonetics and Pronunciation\nAcademic Writing\nPublic Speaking\n\nInterlangues can prepare you for specific College or University Programs with our subject specific vocabulary programs such as:\nEnglish for Law\nEnglish for Engineering\nEnglish for Petroleum Engineering\nEnglish for International Communication\nBusiness English\nand many more.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1 613-236-3764', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://interlangues.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/interlangues1976/', 'https://twitter.com/interlangues76', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Interlangues+Language+School/@45.4137385,-75.6997899,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x4cce05ada0167571:0x4ebe54f87fc59ba2!8m2!3d45.4137348!4d-75.6976012?hl=en_uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/interlangues-language-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/interlangues76/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYtzGOOQxPKXiB9KjSfhLRQ', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Interlangues Language School', 'Interlangues was established in 1976 by Christiane Millet-Alexis, the current C.E.O., and has successfully trained thousands of Canadian and International students. The City of Ottawa, the Department of External Affairs & International Trade and The Department of National Defense have selected Interlangues as their sole provider for all of their language training and testing.', 'Our International English Program is accredited by Languages Canada. Our standards are the same as Canadian Universities and Colleges, but set in a private school and flexible setting. Our main campus is located in the heart of downtown Ottawa, walking distance from main attractions, restaurants, shopping centers and is easily accessible by all bus routes.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
