(192, 'Audencia Nantes School of Management', 1900, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/logo-audencia.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Audencia.jpg', ' Nantes Cedex 3, France', '8 Route de la Jonelière, 44312 Nantes Cedex 3, France', NULL, '\nTOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0', NULL, '7,000 Euro', '\n BACHELORS\n\nBachelor in Management\nBBAEnglish\n\nInternational Management\nEuropean and International Business Management\nManagement\nManagement for Engineers\nFood and Agribusiness Management\nSupply Chain and Purchasing Management\nResponsible Management (MBA)\nAdditional Focuses\n\n\nMaster in European and International Business Management (French, Spanish, English)\nMaster in Management (French)\nSpecialised Masters (French)\nCommunication and Media Studies (French)\n\nEUROMBA (EXECUTIVE & BLENDED)\nMBA IN RESPONSIBLE MANAGEMENT\nEXECUTIVE MBA (FRENCH)  DBA', 'Jean-François Gendron', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33(0)2 40 37 34 34 Q2', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'MBA In Responsible Management 29,000 euros\nMsc In Supply Chain and Purchasing Mgt 14,000 euros\nMsc In Supply Chain and Purchasing Mgt 17,000 euros\nInt', '125 Euro', 'September', 'http://master.audencia.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Audencia', 'https://twitter.com/audencia', 'https://plus.google.com/+audencia', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/audencia', 'https://www.instagram.com/audencia/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/audenciatv', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Audencia Business School', 'Founded in Nantes in 1900, Audencia – from the Latin audientia, meaning “listening”, and audacia, meaning “daring” – was first accredited by EQUIS in 1998 and is ranked amongst the top European business schools. Learn more about Audencia’s quality.', 'UN GLOBAL COMPACT & CSR EXPERTISE\n\nIn 2004, Audencia joined the UN initiative uniting companies, the business world and civil society around 10 universal principles for labour and environmental standards and human rights. We were the first business school in France to join the Global Compact.\n\nSince then, we have been developing and disseminating our expertise in corporate social responsibility (CSR) and integrating it into our research, teaching and internal management.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(193, 'CAVILAM', NULL, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Logo-Cavilam_2012_0.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Cavillam.jpg', 'Vichy, France ', '1 Avenue des Célestins, 03206 Vichy, France\n', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', NULL, '7,000 Euro', 'French courses for all levels, including intensive and super-intensive programmes and one-to-one tuition on its own or combined with an intensive programme\nTailored solutions to meet specific needs (such as business or diplomacy French)\nLanguage classes to prepare for university-level studies\nTraining courses for French as a foreign language teachers\nPreparation for certification in French proficiency (DELF and DALF)\nOther foreign language classes for children and adults', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33470308383', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, 'September', 'http://www.cavilam.com/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Cavilam-Vichy/415609974831', 'https://twitter.com/cavilamvichy', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/cavilam-alliance-fran%C3%A7aise-06713629', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/1280676/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/CAVILAMVICHY', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'CAVILAM', 'About the School\nOur Teaching Methods\nThe team\nCAVILAM – Alliance française is a private institute of higher education in Vichy, in France’s central Auvergne region, within three hours of Paris and two hours of Lyon. The school is open year-round.\nVichy is known as the “Queen of Spas” and has attracted many a tourist keen to sample the wonders of its waters. Its mansions and Art Nouveau opera house combine with the reputed powers of its mineral springs, the appeal of the Allier river and the promise of long walks through leafy parks dating back to the time of Napoleon III to imbue the city with unmatched charm and evoke the perfect embodiment of the French way of life.\nVichy also boasts state-of-the-art sporting facilities situated in splendid natural surroundings.', 'A centre of excellence\nCAVILAM (Centre d’Approches Vivantes des Langues et des Médias) was established in 1964 by the municipality of Vichy and the universities of Clermont-Ferrand. It joined the international Alliance française network in 2012.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(194, 'ECE Paris', 1919, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ECE.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ECE-Paris.jpg', 'Paris, France', '37 Quai de Grenelle, 75015 Paris, France', NULL, 'An International Bachelor’s degree (3 or 4 years) in science or technology (Bachelor of Science or Bachelor of Engineering).\nAll courses have English and/or French requirements. You must provide a proof of the language ability.\nEnglish language tests for all majors\n-IELTS: 6.0 (minimum) OR\n-TOEFL: 83 (iBT)\n-TOEIC: 780\nFrench language tests for majors offered in French\n-B2 level in any of the following tests: TCF, TEF, DELF or DALF   ', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'ENERGY & ENVIRONMENT  QUANTITATIVE FINANCE  HEALTH & TECHNOLOGY  INFORMATION SYSTEMS EMBEDDED SYSTEMS  CONNECTED THINGS  TRANSPORTATION & MOBILITY', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33184140302', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, 'September', 'http://www.ece.fr/school-of-engineering/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ECE.Paris/', 'https://twitter.com/ingenieursece?lang=en', 'https://plus.google.com/101882693187144496156', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/ece-paris-12304', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/280485025/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/IngenieursECE', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ece paris ', 'ECE Paris educates general and high-tech engineers eager to create solutions to today’s most pressing social challenges.\nDuring their studies in France and abroad, ECE Paris students gain the expertise required in all the major sectors: industry, manufacturing, energy, construction, transportation, trade and distribution, finance, insurance, administration, health, education, culture, media, etc.', '10 GOOD REASONS TO ENROLL AT ECE PARIS\n1. A master’s degree in Engineering recognized and accredited by the French Ministry of Higher Education and Research and the Council of Engineers.\n2. An engineering school offering specializations highly demanded in the employment market\n3. An internationally recognized school with 113 agreements in 35 countries including 52 double degrees\n4. Project-based teaching where the value of student projects are emphasized and recognized during the curriculum\n5. Career-focused program where mandatory internships provide the path to successful careers after graduation\n6. Experienced Faculty: highly qualified faculty with extensive industry and research experience\n7. One incubator and three research laboratories\n8. Exceptional student services: International Relations Department and Corporate Relations providing individual attention to our students\n9. Active student life: which is highly encouraged and easily accessible, offering over 20 student clubs and associations\n10. Excellent location: in the heart of Paris, step away from the Eiffel tower', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(195, 'EISTI', 1983, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EISTI.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/eisti1.jpg', ' Cergy, France', ' Avenue du Parc, 95000 Cergy, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'INTERNATIONAL MASTER IN FINANCE  INTERNATIONAL MASTER IN BIGDATA  Mathematics track IT track', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33134251010', 'admission@studymetro.com', '6000 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'https://eisti.fr/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/myEISTI', 'https://twitter.com/myeisti', 'https://plus.google.com/110953483093506838532', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/eisti', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/eisti/', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/eistitv', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'eisti', 'Our charter is made up of four strong values allowing each and every person at the EISTI to flourish during their time here, and after. The charter and all it stands for leaves a mark on our students, notably showing during their professional path and development. Our former students often make reference to the charter, and their networks are sensitive to it. Being an Eistien is a way of being, acting and thinking on a daily basis. With each new school year, the charter is presented to everybody at the school, in order for the school’s philosophy to become completely integrated in their way of thinking, acting and being.', 'PROFESSIONALISM\n\nAppreciating group work\n\nBringing together individual talent and collective success\n\nEnsuring the trust of businesses\n\nOPENNESS\n\nRemaining curious of the lives of others\n\nGoing to others in order to enrich one’s knowledge and sharing one’s own with them\n\nDaring to share\n\nQuestioning oneself \n\nBeing proof of humility;\n\nIgnoring useless assumptions\n\nAvoiding arrogance and self-satisfaction', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(196, 'Emlyon Business School', 1872, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Emylon.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EMLYON-BUSINESS-SCHOOL.jpg', 'Écully, France', '23 Avenue Guy de Collongue, 69130 Écully, France', NULL, 'Admission Requirements:\n- University Degree (minimum Bachelor''s Degree or equivalent)\n- Min 3 years work experience\n- Fluency in at least 2 languages (French is not necessary for Admission)\n- GMAT, GRE or TAGE MAGE Score\n- English proficiency score (TOEIC or TOEFL or IELTS or Cambridge CPE or PTE)\nPlease note:\n- You may apply even if you have not taken the GMAT/GRE/TAGE MAGE test yet.\n- An exemption from a GMAT/GRE/TAGE MAGE test is possible but only under specific conditions.TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', NULL, '7,000 Euro', 'rogrammes\nBACHELOR PROGRAMME\nGlobal BBA Shanghai\nGlobal BBA Saint-Etienne\nGlobal BBA Casablanca\nGlobal BBA Paris\nGRADUATE PROGRAMMES\nMSc in International Hospitality Management\nMSc in Management\nGlobal Entrepreneurship Program\nMSc in Sports Industry Management\nMSc in Luxury Management & Marketing\nSpecialised Programme in Quantitative Finance\nProgrammes taught in French\nEMLYON MBA\nFull-time MBA FULL TIME\nExecutive MBA PART TIME\nPHD PROGRAMME\nPhD Programme\nEXECUTIVE DEVELOPMENT\nAdvanced Management Programme/CPA\nExecutive MBA\nGeneral Management Programme (PGM)\nLeading an activity (DUA)\nOpen programmes\nCorporate Solutions\nPROGRAMMES FOR ENTREPRENEURS\nProgramme I.D.E.A - taught in French\nGlobal Entrepreneurship Program\nSpecialised Master Entreprendre\nAdvanced Management Programme/CPA\nPre incubation / training programme\nIncubation\nASIAN CAMPUS PROGRAMMES\nAsian Campus Programmes\nAFRICA-BASED PROGRAMME\nMsc Finance in Africa - taught in French', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33478337800', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Global Entrepreneurship Program 33,200\nEuropean Master in Mgt (specialisation in finance,marketing,consulting) 18000 per year\nMsc in Luxury Mgt & Mark', '120 Euro', 'September', 'http://www.em-lyon.com/en#', 'https://fr-fr.facebook.com/EMLYONBusinessSchool', 'https://twitter.com/EMLYON', 'https://plus.google.com/+emlyon', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/emlyon-business-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/2466417/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/EMLYON', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'emlyon business school ', 'Since its creation, emlyon business school has been driven by entrepreneurship, innovation and humanism. Our vision and mission are nurtured by our global and digital world. The entrepreneur from emlyon business school is a maker and an early mover. He is an early maker.', 'emlyon business school is a major force in the world of European Business Schools. We are one of the few business schools to hold triple accreditation from Equis, AACSB and AMBA.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(197, 'EPITA', 1984, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EPITA.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Epit.jpg', ' Kremlin Bicêtre Cedex, France', '14/16 Rue Voltaire, 94276 Kremlin Bicêtre Cedex, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Master of Computer Engineering (ME) Master of Computer Science (MSc)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33144080101\n', 'admission@studymetro.com', '12400 Euro', '60 Euro', 'March & September', 'https://www.facebook.com/EPITA.International.Master', 'https://twitter.com/WorldEPITA', 'https://plus.google.com/+epita', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=20389', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/epita/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/EpitaOfficiel', NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'EPITA', 'Founded in 1984, EPITA is a renowned bilingual Graduate School of Computer Engineering situated in Paris. It is a member of IONIS Education Group, the leading private higher education group, with some 20 schools and educational institutions. Thanks to its unique pedagogical approach, EPITA trains its students to become outstanding engineers who boast a solid base of scientific knowledge and the most advanced skills in the digital sector.', 'A computer engineer trained at EPITA has a complete professional profile: as computer technology is omnipresent in all areas of a company, a digital engineer may work in the field of human resources, marketing, communication and even finance. EPITA is ranked among the five top computer engineering schools in France and has developed partnerships with a wide range of companies.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(198, 'ESC RENNES', 1990, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ESC_Rennes.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Esc.jpg', ' Rennes, France', '2 Rue Robert d''Arbrissel, 35065 Rennes, France', NULL, 'IELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Master in Management\nInternational Masters\nExecutive MBA\nBachelor in Management (IBPM)\nBachelor ESLI »\nExchange students\nDoctoral Programmes »\nSummer programme', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33299546363', 'admission@studymetro.com', '13000 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'https://www.esc-rennes.fr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/escrennes/', 'https://twitter.com/escrennes', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/esc-rennes', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/235211625/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ESCRennes', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESC RENNES', 'The world has become a “global village” where economies are closely interrelated, political, social and cultural dimensions tightly interwoven or openly confrontational. This brings considerable opportunities but also greater complexity. One “must prepare for the future by seeing what others cannot (…and) have others follow your direction when there is no map”.(1)', 'Management Schools have to face these new challenges, responding to companies needs, by educating and training students and managers to be the “Responsible Business Entrepreneurs” for tomorrow’s world.\n \nFor Rennes School of Business, it has led to the development of two main priorities: Internationalisation and Innovation.\nThe school intends to prepare Global Responsible Pionneers.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
