est academic standards, EGU focuses on giving individual attention to every student, and providing them with a multi-cultural experience in and out of the classroom.', 'Mission Statement\nEuropean Global University promotes lifelong educational goals of learners, supports workforce development needs of employers, and fosters community involvement by providing a substantive, responsible, and accessible learning environment.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(200, 'INSEEC alpes-savoie', 1992, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INSEEC.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INSEEC1.jpg', ' Le Bourget Du Lac Cedex, France', '12 Avenue du Lac d''Annecy, 73381 Le Bourget Du Lac Cedex, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', '\nAMERICAN BBA INSEEC\nParis       London   San Francisco\nBACHELOR INTERNATIONAL TRADE\n      Chambery      \nINSEEC BACHELOR\nParis       London   San Francisco\nINSEEC BACHELOR IN BUSINESS MARKETING & MANAGEMENT  MSc and MBA programs in Management & Finance\nOverview\nCapital MBA\nMBA Business Diplomacy\nMSc Business, Innovation and Entrepreneurship\nMSc Commercial Engineering & Project Management\nMSc International Business Management\nMSc International Purchasing & Supply Chain Management\nMSc Tourism Marketing & Management\nMBA Finance\nMSc Corporate Finance & Investment Banking\nMSc and MBA programs in Luxury & Wine\nOverview\nMaster Luxury Marketing\nMBA Luxury Brand Communication & Marketing\nMBA Luxury Brand Management, Food and Wine\nMBA Luxury Brand Management, Jewelry & Cosmetics\nMSc Fashion Marketing, Design & Brand Strategies\nMBA Spirits Marketing & Management\nMBA Wine Marketing & Management\nMSc Luxury Hospitality and Event Management\nMSc Luxury Management, Fine Food & Tourism\nMSc and MBA programs in Marketing, Communication & Digital\nOverview\nMaster Digital Marketing & Social Media\nMBA Advertising & Brand Strategy\nMBA Advertising & Public Relations\nMBA Art Direction & Creative Thinking\nMBA Digital Marketing & Social Media\nMBA International Brand Strategy & Marketing\nMBA Marketing & Brand Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33479253254', 'admission@studtmetro.com', 'B.B.A 7850 euros per year\nAsian M.B.A 7500 euros M1 and 7750 euros M2\nLatin American M.B.A 7500 euros M1 and 7750 euros M2\nMaster in Wine Marketing & ', NULL, 'September', 'https://www.inseec.education/', 'https://www.facebook.com/inseecmba', 'https://twitter.com/inseecmba', 'https://plus.google.com/114288534386006596176', 'https://www.linkedin.com/groups/4020117/profile#a11y-content', 'https://www.instagram.com/inseec/    ', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/InseecMBA', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'INSEEC alpes-savoie', 'The campus, located in the St Martin / Republic area, offers an unparalleled quality of life for our students. The banks of the Canal St Martin are popular locations in central Paris, students can easily access pubs and restaurants: conviviality and relaxation are waiting for you!\n\nThe modern and fully renovated campus offers students an environment dedicated to studies and meetings with professionals. All classrooms are connected to WI-FI. The school also features a completely redesigned Bloomberg Trading Room and a Cafeteria.', 'A new-generation Intranet, accessible via the web and via a mobile app, provides students with all necessary information for the conduct of their studies at INSEEC (schedules, access to courses, tips, etc..).', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(201, 'IPAG', 1965, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/logo_ipag_grey.gif', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ipag_paris_550.jpg', ' bd Saint-Germain ,Paris ', '184, bd Saint-Germain 75006 Paris ', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'UNDERGRADUATE PROGRAMME\nBachelor of International Business Management\nIBMP\nPOSTGRADUATE PROGRAMME\nMSc in Business Management (Hanoi)\nDual Degree\nMBA in English\nMBA French\nDBA\nOTHER PROGRAMMES\nExchange\nSummer Programme', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33(0)153633600 ', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelor of Management  \nMBA in Internatinal Trade 7000 euros pa \nMBA in Food Business Management 9000 euros\nMBA in Energy & Sustainable Development M', NULL, 'Bachelor of Management Jan& Sept\nMBA in Internatinal Trade March & Oct\nMBA in Food Business Manageme', 'http://www.ipag.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/IPAGBusinessSchool', 'https://twitter.com/IpagBS', 'https://plus.google.com/+IPAGBusinessSchool', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=20513&trk=edu-cp-title', 'https://www.instagram.com/ipagbusinessschool/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/Ipagcommunication', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'IPAG', 'IPAG Business School has inherited a prestigious history. It was founded in 1965 by Jacques Rueff, a member of the French Academy. It has been continuously enhancing its range of courses since that date. In addition to its Paris campus, it has developed both in Nice and abroad.\n\nIPAG Business School\nIPAG Business School is the only business school to have been founded by a member of the French Academy, the economist Jacques Rueff. In 1965, he founded the Centre de formation supérieure des cadres du commerce et de l’industrie. He set up the school in a prestigious building, which used to house the former Geographical Society. It is the place where Ferdinand de Lesseps drew up the plans for the Panamá Canal in 1880.', 'In 1969, the school changed its name to Institut de préparation à l’administration et à la gestion (Ipag). It was recognised by the State the year after. It has been continually developing since that date: its range of courses has been continuously enhanced. Three campuses have been opened, in Nice (1989), Kunming and Riverside (2012).', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(202, 'ISEP', 1955, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ing_isep_fr_0.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/isep.jpg', 'Paris, France', '28 Rue Notre Dame des Champs, 75006 Paris, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'ISEP offers 3 Specialized Masters in initial or continuing education:\n\nManagement and protection of personal data\nExpert Cloud Computing and SaaS\nand 4 BADGE (s):\n\nLegal practitioner has the Personal Data Protection  \nTechnique practitioner to the Protection of Personal Data\nTechnical Expert Cloud Computing\nProject Manager Cloud Computing   associated preparatory cycle\nInternational Integrated Cycle\nconventional route engineer\nEngineer learning\nDouble degree Audencia\nEngineer by VAE', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33149545200', 'admission@studymetro.com', '13300 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'http://www.isep.fr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ISEP.Paris', 'https://twitter.com/isep', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/institut-sup-rieur-d''electronique-de-paris-i-s-e-p-', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/isep/?hl=en', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ISEPecoleingenieur', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ISEP', 'ISEP is a great school that trains engineers in all digital areas .\n\nThe program combines a solid scientific and technical training in a managerial education appropriate and develops a strong international dimension .\n\nThe degree of ISEP (Master''s degree and authorized by CTI) is for 60 years, a veritable " passport" to employment and provides access to varied careers - scientific, technical, commercial or managerial - in all sectors, in France and abroad ( Aerospace, Automotive, Telecommunications, Health, Finance, Board, Space, etc. ) the ISEP , consistently ranked top of group B is widely popular with businesses who recognize our students for future engineers of the highest level.', 'The educational project of the ISEP is based on a skills-based approach that effectively meets the needs of the professional world and promotes learning situation. The student is placed in the heart of his own training to become the main player via an innovative and highly motivating teaching: project-based learning . This pedagogy helps make the engineering student, operational and able to adapt to business changes in a global economy .', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(203, 'La Rochelle Business School', 1988, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/La-Rochelle.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/La-Rochelle1.jpg', ' La Rochelle, France', '102 Rue de Coureilles, 17000 La Rochelle, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'OUR PEDAGOGICAL PHILOSOPHY\nAcademic excellence\nPersonal development\nLearning through experience\nHumacite\nBACHELOR PROGRAMMES\nBachelor in International Business BBA\nBachelor in Business\nBachelor in Tourism, Hospitality and Event Management\nMASTER IN MANAGEMENT - GRANDE ECOLE PROGRAMME\nMaster in Management - Grande Ecole Programme\nSPECIALISED MBA\nSpecialised MBA :\nMBA Audit and Consultancy\nMBA International Business Strategy\nMBA Purchasing & Supply Chain Management\nSEE ALL THE LINKS\nSCHOOL OF TOURISM\nPresentation of the School\nBachelor Hospitality and Gastronomy management\nBachelor Event and Leisure management\nBachelor Travel and Tourism management\nSEE ALL THE LINKS\nINTERNATIONAL STUDENTS\nBFP (Business Foundation Programme)\nSummer Schools\nFrench Language Institute', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33546517700', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelor in International Business 8900 euros pa\n   \nBachelor in Tourism Management 7400 euros pa\nMBA directly in 2nd Year 10800 Euros\nMBA in Tourism ', '175 Euro', 'September', 'http://www.esc-larochelle.fr/eng', 'https://www.facebook.com/GroupeSupdeCoLaRochelle', 'https://twitter.com/groupesupdecolr', 'https://plus.google.com/110943724979708783142', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sup-de-co-la-rochelle', 'https://www.instagram.com/groupesupdecolr/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/SupDeCoLaRochelle', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'La Rochelle Business School', 'While our primary mission is to deliver high-quality academic skills, we also strongly believe that it is by working on the behaviour and personal fulfilment of the student that we can produce rounded and accomplished managers.\n\nIn an increasingly complex world, our primary aim is to ensure that tomorrow’s managers are human and humanistic, responsible and accountable.\n\nFor this reason, our school endeavours to transmit to all those involved — students, teachers and administrative staff — the core values it holds:\n\nRespect, tolerance and consideration\nCommitment and responsibility\nHonesty and integrity\nTeamwork and solidarity\nOpen-mindedness towards the world and to other\nResponsible management (link to Environmental and Social Responsibility)', 'La Rochelle Business School can also be identified by its genuine support for social and cultural diversity. This can be seen in our participation in the social mobility programme (link to the Passerelle Ascenseur Social website) run by the Passerelle association. Because society is diverse, there should be more than just one profile for managers; they should come from all walks of life and be involved in the most varied projects and experiences.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(204, 'Skema France', 2009, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Skeema.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/SKEMA-At-home-worldwide.jpg', ' Valbonne, France', 'Sophia Antipolis, 60 Rue Fedor Dostoïevski, 06902 Valbonne, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor in Aeronautical Science & Management\nBachelor in Management & Business Administration\nBachelor in Marketing & Business Development\nBachelor in Technological Innovation & Management  (Mechanical )\nBachelor in Mgt of Marine Environment & Sustainable Development\nBachelor in Civil & Environmental Engineering\nMs in Auditing, Accounting & Management & Information Systems\nMsc in Corporate Financial Management\nMsc in Financial Market & Investments\nMsc in International Marketing & Business Development\nMsc in Strategic Event Management & Tourism Management\nMsc in Luxury & Fashion management\nMsc in Web- Marketing & International Project managemnt\nMsc in International Business\nMsc in Enterpreneurship & Innovation for a Sustainable world\nMsc in Strategic Human Resource Management\nMsc in Business Consulting & Information Systems Management\nMsc in Supply Chain Management & Purchasing\nMsc in Project & Programme Management & Business Development\nMsc in Business & Economics\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33493954444', 'admission@studymetro.com', '15000 Euro', '120 Euro', 'Jan,Feb,March& Sept', 'http://www.skema.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SKEMA.Business.School', 'https://twitter.com/Skema_BS', 'https://plus.google.com/+skema', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=22499&goback=%2Epth_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1&trk=edu-up-nav-menu-homecom', 'https://www.instagram.com/skema_bs/', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/skema', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Skema France', 'The mission and values on which SKEMA has based its strategy are completely in line with world economic developments.\n\nTo offer training and guidance to men and women, students and practitioners, so that they can develop both personally and professionally. SKEMA is open to people from all backgrounds who have strong potential and who respect the values of ethics and responsibility, so that they are able to:\n\nMake their mark in organisations of all sizes in any country or region in the multicultural context of the globalised economy?\nContribute to their organisations’ sustainble development and performance through their sense of innovation, their technical skills and international cross-cultural competence.', 'SKEMA was founded in 2009 as a result of the merger between the Ecole Supérieure de Commerce, Lille and CERAM Business School, Sophia Antipolis. The Lille school had been ?founded in 1892 and CERAM in 1963.\n\n\nSKEMA is a member of the Conférence des Grandes Ecoles. The school was approved by the French Ministry of Higher Education and Research, as an EESPIG (Private Establishment for Higher Education declared to be of pubic usefulness). This official status was conferred on 6 July 2015 and declared in the Bulletin Officiel on 23 July 2015.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(205, 'ISC ', 1963, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/logo_ecole_management_isc.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ISC.jpg', ' Boulevard du Fort de Vaux, Paris, France', '22 Boulevard du Fort de Vaux, 75017 Paris, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor\nBachelor in Business\nMBA programs\nMBA Fragrances and Cosmetics\nMBA International Finance\nMBA International Project Development Management\nMBA Luxury Hotel Management\nMBA Luxury Marketing', NULL, '18400', NULL, NULL, 'Off Campus', '33140539999', 'admission@studymetro.com', '12900 Euro', NULL, 'January & September', 'http://international.iscparis.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ISCParisSchool', 'https://twitter.com/iscparisschool', 'https://plus.google.com/+iscparis', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/isc-paris', 'https://www.instagram.com/iscparis/?hl=en', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ISCParis', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ISC Paris', 'To produce true professionals of a high academic standard who will be equipped to meet global business challenges and be valued by their employers. We specifically prepare our students to successfully navigate the pressing challenges facing global business and society by providing managerial training of a high academic standard supported by applied research, intellectual contributions and real-world exposure to other business cultures.\n\nWithin this overall framework, our mission is to :\n\n• Support students to take responsibility for their own training, develop their leadership ability and prepare for the global context through exposure to international issues.\n• Carry out quality production of intellectual contributions that advance knowledge of business, management practice and learning pedagogy in a stimulating and enriching environment.\n• Give students discernment for responsible management, sense of duty and develop their decision-making skills through practical, professional experience in an inspiring environment.', 'Established in 1963, ISC Paris – Business School is committed to providing business students with the high quality management skills necessary to operate and perform in a global environment.\n\nISC Paris is part of the highly selective French “Grandes Ecoles” recruiting system, which groups higher education establishments that operate outside the sphere of Universities. In France, only 50 management schools are entitled to run a “Grande Ecole” program with a Masters in Management, and a mere 30 of these are, like ISC Paris, members of the prestigious Conférence des Grandes Ecoles.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(206, 'EICAR', 1972, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/eicar.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/visuel_bandeau_eicar_exchange.jpg', ' Saint-Denis, France', '50 Avenue du Président Wilson, 93210 Saint-Denis, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Master of Fine Arts in Film & Television\nMaster Creative Producing\nBachelor of Fine Arts program in filmmaking with 5 Specializations –\n Directing, Screenwriting, Cinematography, Producing and Editing.\nThe One year Filmmaking program -introduction to the essentials of filmmaking', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33149981111', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Fast Track program 13,100 euros\nBachelors program 12,650 euros per year\nMaster''s program 18,950 euros per year\n', NULL, 'March & September', 'http://www.eicar-international.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/EICAR.Paris', 'https://twitter.com/ecoleEICAR', 'https://plus.google.com/115729471427490372693', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/eicar-155072', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/170514/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/EICARofficial', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'EICAR', 'EICAR, The International Film and Television School of Paris, was founded in 1972. The School has developed over the years to become a major European film and television school offering students from all over the world the largest range available today of up to date hands on practical education in filmmaking both in English or French.\n\n ', 'Our Mission is to prepare our students \nfor the international job market \nWe are committed to helping students acquire the professional artistic and technical skills necessary in order to enter and build a career in the audiovisual industry.\nWe are committed to providing hands on training. Our students are taught to be doers: over half the syllabus in any course is therefore assigned to practical shoots and film assignments.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(207, 'ESLSCA', 1949, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ESLSCA.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ESLSCA1.jpg', ' Bougainville, Paris, France', '1 Rue Bougainville, 75007 Paris, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'General MBA\nMBA in Business Communication\nMBA in International Marketing\nMBA in International Business\nMBA in Luxury', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33145513259', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Msc in International Business 9000 euros\nMsc in International Marketing 9000 euros\nGeneral MBA (GMAT Mandatory) 10,000 euros\n', NULL, 'Jan, March& Oct', 'http://www.eslsca.fr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Paris-ESLSCA-Business-School-335260133233/', 'https://twitter.com/ESLSCAparis', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/eslsca-business-school', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESLSCA', 'ur Department houses all graduate programs in English that the ESLSCA offers in Paris. We currently offer the following programs: the general MBA and the Pre-MBA, the Specialized MBA in International Marketing (MIM), the Specialized MBA in Business Communication (MBC), the Specialized MBA in International Business (MIB) as well as Graduate Certificates. The Executive MBA program began on 2010.', 'Established in 1996, the general MBA is a rigorous full-time 12-16 month program designed to prepare students for business leadership. The Pre-MBA, established in 2001, is a 12-week intensive program designed for nonnative English speakers. It is offered once a year in January.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(208, 'TOULOUSE', 1903, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/TBS.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Toulouse-group-at-graduate-school-2014.jpg', 'Toulouse, France', ' 20 Boulevard Lascrosses, 31068 Toulouse, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor in Management Program\nMaster of Business Administration (MBA)\nDoctorate of Business Administration (DBA)\nMaster in Management Program\n\nMSc. Banking & International Finance\nMSc. Supply Chain And Lean managEment (SCALE)\nSM2 Cluster\nMSc. Marketing, Management & Communication\nMSc. Sports, Marketing & Management\nMSc. Hospitality & Tourism Marketing & Management\nMSc. Digital Intelligence & Marketing Analytics (DIMA)\nMSc. Finance Barcelona\nMSc. Marketing Barcelona\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33561294949', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelors In Management 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Finance 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Business 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Marketing 7200 Euros p.a\n', '100 Euro', 'September', 'http://www.tbs-education.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ToulouseBusinessSchool', 'https://twitter.com/ToulouseBS', 'https://plus.google.com/+tbs-education-fr', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/toulouse-business-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/toulousebs/', 'https://www.youtube.com/toulousebs', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'TOULOUSE', 'Three Campuses, Three Accreditations, One School Open to the World\nProfessionals today have to keep pace with the demands of a fast-changing business world. Toulouse Business School (TBS) is dedicated to providing its students with the analytical skills, professional network and agility needed to adapt, innovate, and anticipate change. As part of an economic, cultural, and educational center at the heart of Europe, our students have the knowledge and network to succeed wherever their career takes them.\n\nThrough a broad core curriculum and multiple specialization areas, business education at TBS builds practical skills for the business world of today – and tomorrow. Discover TBS and its multilingual, multicultural, and interdisciplinary environment:', 'Specialized Business Education – At the core of TBS is our wide range of undergraduate and graduate degree programs. We offer programs taught in French, English, or Spanish in the fields of Management, Business, Marketing, Finance, and Aerospace Management. We also offer elite Executive Education and specialized programs.  TBS also functions as a thriving center for business research. \nGlobal Network – With 75 nationalities represented on our three campuses in Toulouse, Barcelona, and Casablanca, and two sites developing in Paris and London, as well as 160 Partner Universities worldwide, TBS is a global institution with a welcoming environment for international students.\nQuality Assurance and Rankings – TBS offers internationally recognized degrees and is part of the prestigious 1% of business schools with the “triple crown” of accreditations: EQUIS, AACSB, and AMBA. TBS ranks among the top business schools in France, and our Master in Management program is among Europe’s Top 20 (Financial Times, 2012 (link is external)).\nDynamic Corporate Relations – Our distinguished research faculty features a teaching staff of 1,200 high-level professionals with diverse experience in business sectors. In addition, students in Toulouse can take advantage of our institutional connections to over one hundred multinational corporations including Airbus Group, Alcatel Space, Motorola, Siemens, and Sony.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(209, 'VATEL ', 1981, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1427113286logo_vatel_school_0.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Vatel.jpg', ' Nîmes, France', '140 Rue Vatel, 30900 Nîmes, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor Vatel\nInternational Hotel Management\nMBA Vatel\nInternational Hotel Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33466625706', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelors in International Hotel Management 11,800 euros per year\nMasters in International Hotel Management  \nFoundation course(for those who are from', '330 Euro', 'March & September', 'http://www.vatel.fr/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/vatelschool', 'https://twitter.com/vatelschool', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=356046', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ecolehotelierevatel', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'VATEL ', 'Vatel trains operational managers and senior executives in the International Hotel and Tourism Management industries.\n\nWith 35 years of experience, our campuses located throughout the world convey the same internationally targeted courses to 7,000 students based on the tried and tested mixture of theoretical university courses followed by professional experience. ', 'This concept has a provable track record: our 29,000 alumni work in the most beautiful hotels on earth and 80% of them work in the hotel and tourist management fields. Their jobs include, amongst others, functions of General Manager of a hotel chain or individual hotel, Hotel Manager, Sales Manager, Marketing, Human Resources or Financial Management, Public Relations or Special Events Manager, Auditor, Housekeeper, Front Desk Manager, just to name a few. As for the other 20%, they are recruited in other fields, especially in luxury brand management, where decision-makers are convinced by their skills and know-how.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(210, 'ESAIP', 1987, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esaip_angers4.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esaip_angers4.jpg', 'Saint-Barthélemy-d''Anjou, France', '18 Rue du 8 Mai 1945, 49124 Saint-Barthélemy-d''Anjou, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'PROGRAMMES\nENGINEERING PROGRAMMES\nDigital Engineering – Computer Science & Networks\nRisk, Health, Safety and Environmental Management\n BSC. & MSC. PROGRAMMES\nBachelor International Data Manager\nMSS Security Science\nM.Sc Digital Engineering & Big Data\n SHORT PROGRAMMES\nERASMUS Mobility\nSummer or Winter Programmes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33241966510', 'admission@studymetro.com', '5550 Euro ', NULL, 'March & September', 'https://www.esaip.org/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/groupeesaip', 'https://twitter.com/groupeesaip', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/MaChaineESAIP', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESAIP', '"The goal of the esaip group since 1989 has been to train men and women for the jobs of the future, in order for them to evolve at an international level and gain strong adaptation capabilities for the world of business. The know-how « Made in esaip » has proved itself throughout the years, most notably through international openings and the individual follow-up provided to every student\nand trainee. Founded on Lasallian values of accessibility for all to higher education, the mission of the esaip group is to help each of our students and trainees to achieve their goals.\nWe take up this daring challenge every year with success."', 'ESAIP is a Graduate school of Engineering proposing a generalist, broad-based 3 years course, starting at a Bac+2 level or based 5 years course, starting at a Bac level. ESAIP offers two Diplomas at Angers and Grasse:\n• Computer science and networks\n• Safety, environment and industrial risk managment.\n\nThe graduate school of Engineering is authorized by the “Commission des Titres d’Ingénieurs”, EUR-ACE label, member of the “Conférence des Grandes Ecoles”.\n\n ', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(211, 'EMN', 1990, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EMN.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Emn-nannetes.jpg', ' Nantes, France', '4 Rue Alfred Kastler, 44300 Nantes, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Msc in Sustainable Nuclear Energy & Waste Mgt.\n(SNEWM ) ( NEP or ANWM)\nMsc in Project Mgt for Envt & Energy Eng (PM3E )\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33251858100', 'admission@studymetro.com', '15000 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'http://www.mines-nantes.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/minesnantes/', 'https://twitter.com/minesnantes', 'https://plus.google.com/+MinesNantesEcole', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=12335', 'https://www.instagram.com/minesnantes/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/minesnantes', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'EMN', 'Founded in 1990, the Ecole des Mines de Nantes is located on a 15 hectare site in the heart of Atlanpole, the Nantes technology park. In its modern buildings, engineering students benefit from an ideal learning environment with state-of-the-art facilities.', 'Mines de Nantes forms engineers and researchers to serve and anticipate the needs of industry. Its close relationship with the corporate world offers a double guarantee: to companies, both SMEs and large groups from diverse sectors, that they will always find graduates from the School with profiles necessary for their development; and to students, the certainty of exciting careers.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(212, 'BEM', NULL, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/BMS.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/bembms.jpg', 'Talence - France', '680 Cours Libération,33405 Talence - France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', '\nPROGRAMMES\nMASTER IN MANAGEMENT GRANDE ECOLE\nPOST HIGH SCHOOL PROGRAMMES\nInternational BBA\nDESIGN SCHOOL\nInnovation & Design Thinking\nMBA PROGRAMMES\nGlobal MBA\nANTAI-KEDGE EMBA Shanghai\nEURO-ASIA DBA PROGRAMME\nSPECIALIZED PROGRAMMES\nISLI - Global supply chain management\nMAI - Innovation and International purchasing\nSPORT - International Sport & Event Management\nMARITIME - Commercial & Logistics Optimization\nMSC In Wine and Spirits Management\nFINANCE - Corporate Finance\nMARKETING\nInternational Business\nINTERNATIONAL BUSINESS FROM EUROPE TO ASIA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33(0)556845555', 'admission@studymetro.com', '12500 Euro', '120 Euro', 'September', 'http://www.kedgebs.com/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/kedgebs', 'https://twitter.com/KedgeBS', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/groups/4656213/profile', 'https://www.instagram.com/kedgebs/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/KedgeBS', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'BEM', 'KEDGE Business School is an independent non-profit organisation founded on July 1st 2013 by Chambers of Commerce and Industry of Bordeaux and Marseille.\n\nIt is governed by a Board of Directors comprising of business leaders and representatives of local authorities.\n\nThe Board of Directors is strutured into 5 committees holds 65% of the voting rights.', NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(213, 'ESC Dijon / Burgundy School', 1899, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esc_logo_groupe_1297333068.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ESC1-dijon.jpg', ' Dijon, France', '29 Rue Sambin, 21000 Dijon, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', '\nBachelor Marketing&Business\nMaster in Management - Grande Ecole ProgrammeMSc in Advanced Corporate Finance\n\nMSc Arts & Cultural Management\n\nMSc in Global Marketing & Negotiation\n\nMSc in International Business Development\n\nMSc in Wine Management \n\nMSc in Wine Business\n\nThe MS Commerce International des Vins et Spiritueux       The MS Management des Entreprises Culturelles et Industries Créatives', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33380725900', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Msc in International Business Development 9800 euros\nMsc in International Management 9800 euros\nMsc in Wine Business 11,380 euros\nMsc in Wine Manageme', 'Msc in International Business Development 100 Euros\nMsc in International Management 100 Euros\nMsc in Wine Business 100 Euros\nMsc in Wine Management 10', 'September', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/escdijon/?v=wall', 'https://twitter.com/escdijon', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/esc-dijon', 'https://www.instagram.com/escdijon/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/dijonesc', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESC Dijon / Burgundy School', 'Founded in 1899, Burgundy School of Business is a leading teaching and research school belonging to the network of top French academic institutions in management.\n\nWith our deep commitment to the values of responsibility, openness and creativity, we place entrepreneurial management firmly at the centre of our teaching and research mission: to train managers ready to act as entrepreneurs in both business and society at large.\n\nOn the strength of its illustrious history, its values and its organisation, and thanks to the support of companies and institutional authorities of the Burgundy region, Burgundy School of Business has set itself:\n\n- Among the top French management schools, with a strong international dimension\n- As a reference European management institute in the areas of expertise in which Burgundy School of Business excels\n- As a major academic force in entrepreneurial management.\n\nCome and join us in Burgundy!', 'Entrepreneurial Management for Business and Society\nThe School''s mission is to provide current and future managers with high quality education supported by research activities, and to contribute to the development of the region''s economy.\n\n\nOur management education programmes are entrepreneurial and internationally focused, allowing students to acquire professional expertise integrating the needs of the business world and corporate social responsibility.\n\n\n ', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
