of its professional status and qualification with the title International Manager in the Luxury and Fashion Industries validation at level 1 for a 4 […]', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(215, 'ESC Clermont', 1919, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esc_clermont.gif', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esc-clermont.jpg', 'Clermont-Ferrand, France', '4 Boulevard Trudaine, 63000 Clermont-Ferrand, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor program\nBachelor in International Management\n \nMaster in Management\nMaster in Management (Grand Ecole Program)\n \nMaster of Science\nMSc Control, Audit & Corporate Finance\nMSc International Business Development\nMSc International Project Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33473982424', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Msc in International Business Development 11000 euros\nMsc in International Project Management 11000 euros\nMsc in Finance & Auditing 11000 euros\nMaster', '175 Euro', 'September', 'http://www.esc-clermont.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/escclermont', 'https://twitter.com/escclermont', 'https://plus.google.com/100043044165476380960?cfem=1', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/esc-graduate-school-of-management', 'https://www.instagram.com/esc_clermont/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPzI8GzEW52PI9MXYTx2_mw', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESC Clermont', 'The Ecole Supérieure de Commerce de Clermont has made a solid place for itself since its creation in 1919. Under the patronage of the Ministry of Commerce, the city of Clermont-Ferrand, the Conseil Général du Puy-de-Dôme (General Council), the Chamber of Commerce and several companies in partnership with the General Council, the ESC Clermont welcomed a first class of 76 students. Since then, more than 11 000 men and women from all walks of life have trodden the grounds of the Trudaine campus.', 'To train lucid and responsible managers, entrepreneurs and leaders :\n\n• Possessing fundemental knowledge in Management.\n\n• Capable of understanding the complexity and the stakes of the economic and business environment where creativity and innovation are keys to successful decision making, and successful actions.\n\n• Who create value on the economic, social and business fronts.\n\nWe accompany our students towards professional excellence using efficient and original methods.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(216, 'IFAM', NULL, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/IFAM_logo.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/IFAM_BUSINESS_SCHOOL.jpg', ' Paris, France', '19 rue Cépré, 75015 Paris, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'BBA      MBA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', NULL, 'admission@studymetro.com', 'BBA 6000 euros pa\nMsc in International Business  8500 euors\nMBA ( Gmat Mandatory ) 10000 euros\n', NULL, 'March & Sept', 'http://www.ifam.edu/en/', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ifam-business-school', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'IFAM', 'OUR MISSION\nIFAM Business School students are encouraged to develop competencies in :\n\nLeadership and interpersonal communication,\nProblem solving and analysis,\nFast learning,\nApplying critical thinking to Management in a global context. ', 'OUR OBJECTIVES\nAn academic tradition that combines scholarly excellence with continuing interaction with business leaders and current management issues.\nA culture that is based on merit and that is congenial to people of widely varying ethnicities, and national backgrounds.\nA tradition and commitment to the importance of a global perspective and ethical behavior in the conduct of business. ', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(217, 'EHESP', 1945, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EHESP.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ehesp.jpg', ' Rennes, France', '15 avenue du Professeur Léon-Bernard - CS 74312, 35043 Rennes, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Public', '7,000 Euro', 'Master of public health\nEuropubhealth: European Public Health Masters course of study\nMaster in Analysis and Management of Health Establishments\nMaster of law, health and ethics\nMaster in Health Education for Children, Adolescents and Young Adults\nMaster in Health Care Assessment\nMaster in Youth : policies and care\nMaster in public health and environmental risks\nMaster in administration of public health policies and programmes\nMaster in Public Health: Social Sciences Pathway\nMaster in clinical nursing sciences\nMaster in Disability and Social Participation\nPost-Master in Public Health\nPost-Master in Biomedical Equipment\nPost-Master in Engineering and Management of Health, Environment and Workplace Risks (IMR-SET)\nPost-Master in Health Technology Engineering and Management\nPost-Master’s in Health Management\nDoctoral Network\nDirector of health, welfare and care establishments (CAFDES)Preparation for competitive entrance examinations\nHospital Nursing Administration Program\nPublic Health Medical Inspector Program\nPublic Health Pharmacist Inspector Program\nSchool Physician program\nEnvironmental Health Administration Program\nPublic Health technician Program\nHealth Care Institution Management Program\nSocial Care Institution Management Program\nHealth Care Institution Administration Program\nHospital engineer Program\nPublic Health and Social Welfare Inspector Program\nRegional occupational physician Program\nPublic Health engineering manager Program', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33 2 99 02 22 00', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Master of public Health 6000p.a\nExecutive Health MBA 16000\nEuropean Health Management 8000 p.a\n', NULL, 'September', 'www.ehesp.fr/en/\n', 'https://www.facebook.com/EHESP', 'https://twitter.com/EHESP', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ehesp---school-of-public-health', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'EHESP', 'The EHESP is a public establishment with a dual role of education and research into public health and social welfare. It encourages synergy between the disparate cultures of public health and management.', 'The EHESP School of Public Health was set up to provide a school of higher public health studies in France. The organization implemented serves the strategic guidelines of the institution presented in the objective and performance contract for the period 2014 to 2018.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
