t the exception. It''s a world of creativity; inspiration and ambition where learning becomes lifelong process and our group of institutions and affiliated hospitals provide rigorous academic programs and evidence -based training. The access to modern day technology by empowering the vision to change education and learning process for the better future.\n"We call this greater ambitious project as Premier Hopkin!!! "\nPremier Hopkins International is holding and operational body of group of International Medical & Health Science Institutions and Teaching Hospitals in different parts of the world. Its majority of operations are in Saint Lucia, USA, Ireland, India and few African countries. Premier Hopkins group of educational Institutions develop the next generation leaders in the area of medicine, public health and biomedical Science. These institutions are independently operated under the PH Group. Hopkins Foundation International  (HFI) supports Premier Hopkins Group Educational and research activities. HFI is leading financial supporter and technology partner of Premier Hopkins; intern Premier supports all the philanthropic and educational activities of HFI.Innovation is the rule, not the exception. It''s a world of creativity, inspiration and ambition where learning becomes lifelong process and our group of institutions and affiliated hospitals provide rigorous academic programs and evidence -based training. The access to modern day technology by empowering the vision to change education and learning process for the better future.\n“We call this greater ambitious project as Premier Hopkin!!! ”\nPremier Hopkins International is holding and operational body of group of International Medical & Health Science Institutions and Teaching Hospitals in different parts of the world. Its majority of operations are in Saint Lucia, USA, Ireland, India and few African countries. Premier Hopkins group of educational Institutions develop the next generation leaders in the area of medicine, public health and biomedical Science. These institutions are independently operated under the PH Group. Hopkins Foundation International  (HFI) supports Premier Hopkins Group Educational and research activities. HFI is leading financial supporter and technology partner of Premier Hopkins; intern Premier supports all the philanthropic and educational activities of HFI.\nStudents choose PHU, because of our faculty, curriculum and technologically advanced campus, and our well-earned reputation for providing the education that enables our students to pass their licensing exams.\nThe accomplishments of our MD & ADN graduates are a testament to the quality of our curriculum, dedicated faculty, and excellent facilities at our Saint Lucia campus in the Caribbean.\nOur vision pushes the boundaries of discovery, transforms healthcare, advances medical education and creates hope for humanity. Together, we will deliver the promise of medicine, which is key to the healthy world.\nPremier Hopkins International is committed towards offering affordable high quality medical education with global expansion through innovative business strategies and healthcare solutions.\nPremier Hopkins International has recently acquired educational institutions owned by American International Medical University that specialized in medical, nursing and other health care programs with its current operations in St Lucia, United States and Ireland.\nPHU is a new generation health care education and service provider, which has partnered with the Government of Saint Lucia. PHU offers a variety of programs at its Gros-Islet campus in Saint Lucia.\n? To prepare medical and nursing students to meet challenges in the field of modern medicine.\n? To achieve global identity through innovative educational methods.\n? To take care of the health of the general public by training future physicians in the most current and advanced medical treatments.\n? To contribute to the well being of humanity by teaching students to practice medicine in accordance with high ethical values, with the greatest appreciation for human life.\n? To provide the best environment conducive to the education, health and welfare of our students and community.\nPreparing Medical and Nursing students to meet the challenges in the continually advancing health industry and to provide quality health care to all those in need and bringing health care innovation to serve humanity', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
