com', '£12,250', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.mdx.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/MiddlesexUniversity', 'https://twitter.com/middlesexuni', 'https://plus.google.com/+middlesexuniversity', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/middlesex-university-12616', 'https://www.instagram.com/MiddlesexUniversity/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/MiddlesexUniVideo?feature=watch', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Middlesex University', 'There are many ways we support our local communities, from offering students and staff volunteering opportunities to our considerable contribution through our research, teaching, business and community partnerships.\n\nAs a charity, it''s our privilege to be able to provide a university education to anyone interested in furthering their study, and we offer a staggering wealth of activity to support it.\n\nCritical to our success is continuing to develop a lasting and supportive relationship with the Council, and the wider community, of the London Borough of Barnet. Fostering these partnerships is also one of our main key strategic objectives.\n\nWith more than 25,000 students studying at our campus in London, we''re helping to contribute more than £242m to the local economy (according to latest figures), while supporting an estimated 3,000 jobs.', 'Building effective relationships is essential for any business, whether it is with customers, clients or organisations. From lifelong associations with our students and alumni to facilitating networks between the professional and academic worlds, Middlesex University Business School brings people together to create and share knowledge and experience.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
