 NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 1484 422288', 'admission@studymetro.com', '£12000', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.hud.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/huddersfielduniversity', 'https://twitter.com/HuddersfieldUni', 'https://plus.google.com/+huddersfielduniversity', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/university-of-huddersfield', 'https://www.instagram.com/huddersfielduni/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/hudduni', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'University of Huddersfield', 'Successful, innovative and modern – welcome to the University of Huddersfield\nWhatever you aim to do in life, it pays to get a good education. And with high standards of teaching and learning and excellent facilities that''s exactly what our students can expect from the University of Huddersfield. Based right in the town centre and at the heart of the local community, we help thousands of people, from school leavers to those returning to education after a gap, achieve their goals each year.', 'Why do over 23,000 students choose to study at Huddersfield?\nExcellence\nThe University of Huddersfield is a growing centre of research and excellence and we always push the boundaries of knowledge. Our academic staff are continually rated as providing high quality teaching in an exciting and stimulating environment. We are proud to be rated as number one in the UK for our assessment and feedback as well as being top ten in England for student satisfaction.\n\nEmployment\nWe have an impressive record for graduate employment, with 94% of our undergraduate and 93% of postgraduate students in work or further study six months after graduating. We have excellent links with industry and every year over 2,000 students take part in work placements. We are top in Yorkshire for graduate employability and students can expect a starting salary on average of £19,500.  \n\nEnjoyable\nMillions of pounds have been spent on campus development over the past five years, making sure our students have access to some of the best facilities in the country. Our campus also has a vibrant social scene and we have a very active Students’ Union with more than 70 clubs and societies.\n\nEnterprising\nThe University is growing its reputation as a leader in the field of Enterprise. In 2012 the University was awarded the prestigious Times Higher Education Entrepreneurial University of the Year and followed this up in 2013 when we were awarded two Queen’s Awards for Enterprise. We have helped a number of graduates to set up their own successful businesses and have a fantastic Enterprise Team who are here to help you with your ideas and make sure they get off the ground. Our state-of-the-art 3M Buckley Innovation Centre is a great hub for students who wish to set up their own business and provides a great opportunity to network with other students and local businesses.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(320, 'University of Leicester', 1957, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Colour-University-of-Leicester-Logo.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/leicester_1.jpg', ' Leicester , United Kingdom', 'University Rd, Leicester LE1 7RH, United Kingdom', NULL, 'Overall IELTS grade of 6.5 with a minimum of 6.0 in each component, or equivalent.', 'Public', '£10,000', 'https://le.ac.uk/courses', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 116 252 2522', 'admission@studymetro.com', '£18000', NULL, NULL, 'https://le.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/UniofLeicester', 'https://twitter.com/uniofleicester', 'https://plus.google.com/117567742134339880689', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/university-of-leicester-12707', 'https://www.instagram.com/uniofleicester/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/UniversityLeicester', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'University of Leicester', 'Discovering innovative ways to change the world for the better\n\nOur university was founded almost a hundred years ago in the aftermath of the Great War. The men and women who built this new institution hoped that it would be not only a living memorial to the darkness of their recent past, but a beacon of hope for the future. Their aim was that sacrifices made in war should be commemorated through education and research that would change the world for the better.', 'We are delivering this ambition.\n\nWe have launched a new strategic plan, which sets out our vision to pioneer a distinctive new elite of research-intensive universities. Take a look at the Strategic Plan webpages to find out how we intend to do this.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(321, 'University of Lincoln', 1992, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/UoL-logo-general-use-white-background.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lincoln-campus.jpg', ' Lincoln , United Kingdom', ' Brayford Pool, Lincoln LN6 7TS, United Kingdom', NULL, 'Overall IELTS grade of 6.5 with a minimum of 6.0 in each component, or equivalent.', 'Public', '£10,000', 'http://www.lincoln.ac.uk/home/studyatlincoln/undergraduatecourses/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 1522 882000', 'admission@studymetro.com', '£12000', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lincoln.ac.uk/home/', 'https://www.facebook.com/universityoflincoln', 'https://twitter.com/unilincoln', 'https://plus.google.com/+universityoflincoln', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/university-of-lincoln', 'https://www.instagram.com/unilincoln/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/UniversityofLincoln', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'University of Lincoln', 'Since being opened by Her Majesty the Queen, the University of Lincoln has put students at the heart of everything we do, while climbing more places in university league tables than almost any other institution.\n\nWorld-class teaching and research\n\nThe University has established an international reputation for the quality of teaching and research, with academics and students working together on major projects across areas as varied as cancer treatment, water conservation and low-carbon technology. ', 'High student satisfaction\n\nThe University of Lincoln has some of the most satisfied students in the UK. Lincoln is 11th in the UK for student satisfaction in the National Student Survey (NSS) 2016. In addition, Lincoln has been ranked number one in a range of NSS subject areas including Zoology, Transport and Travel, Design, Biochemistry, and Animal Science.\n\nHistoric city centre location\n\nThe University of Lincoln’s award-winning campus provides a modern, student-centred environment on the picturesque Brayford Pool marina, where everything you need is either on campus or just a short walk away in the city centre. With its medieval castle and one of the finest cathedrals in Europe, Lincoln is steeped in history and home to galleries, cinemas, shopping, restaurants, bars and nightclubs.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
