ividual highlights of the REF 2014 results include: \n\nSussex History was the highest rated History submission in the UK for the quality of its research outputs \nThe Sussex English submission rose from 31st to 9th across the UK since the last research assessment exercise in 2008\n84 per cent of the University’s research impact in Psychology was rated as the top possible grade, 4* \nSussex Geography had the most 4* rated research impact of any Geography submission across the UK.\nOverall, the University was placed 36th (of multi-disciplinary institutions) by GPA.', 'Campus life\nSussex has one of the most beautiful campus locations in Britain. Situated in rolling parkland on the edge of Brighton, the campus combines award-winning architecture with green open spaces. The campus is surrounded by the South Downs National Park, but just a few minutes away from the lively city of Brighton & Hove.\n\nDesigned by Sir Basil Spence, the buildings that make up the heart of the campus were given listed building status in 1993. Falmer House is one of only two educational buildings in the UK to be Grade I listed in recognition of its exceptional interest.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(325, 'Warnborough College (UK)', 1973, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/warnborough.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/warnborough1.jpg', 'Canterbury , United Kingdom', '18 Lower Bridge St, Canterbury CT1 2LG, United Kingdom', NULL, 'Overall IELTS grade of 6.5 with a minimum of 6.0 in each component, or equivalent.', 'Private', '£10,000', 'Business Management\n\nDiploma in Business Management (Level 4)\nHigher Diploma in Business Management (Level 5)\nGraduate Diploma in Business Management (Level 6)\nPostgraduate Diploma in Business Management (Level 7)\nHuman Resource Management\n\nHigher Diploma in Human Resource Management (Level 5)\nGraduate Diploma in Human Resource Management (Level 6)\nMarketing\n\nDiploma in Marketing (Level 4)\nHigher Diploma in Marketing (Level 5)\nGraduate Diploma in Marketing (Level 6)\nTravel, Tourism, Hospitality\n\nDiploma in Travel, Tourism and Hospitality Management (Level 4)\nHigher Diploma in Travel, Tourism and Hospitality Management (Level 5)\nGraduate Diploma in Travel, Tourism and Hospitality Management (Level 6)\nDiploma in Medical Sciences\n\nCreative Workshops\n\nCorporate Training\n\nMini MBA\nVocational and Job Skills', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 1227 762107', 'admission@studymetro.com', '£', NULL, NULL, 'http://warnborough.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Warnborough-College-UK-1443803552506325/', 'https://twitter.com/warnborough', 'https://plus.google.com/114362408378211660689', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/warnborough-college', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/warnborough-college', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/warnboroughcollege', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Warnborough College (UK)', 'Warnborough College is an accredited British College for Adult Education based in the historic university city of Canterbury. Its roots lie deep in the Oxford tradition of quality academic programmes, personal mentoring, love of learning and intellectual curiosity. Warnborough provides study options leading to British qualifications and career needs: University pathways, English language courses, and corporate and vocational training. Courses are taught in Canterbury, at partner campuses around the world, and through distance learning or blended learning.', 'Thousands of students have gone on to further studies at other educational institutions worldwide, and forged successful careers in all fields. A Warnborough education can be experienced through study here in Canterbury, by distance learning, by blended learning, or through one of our Academic Partners. With our corporate partners, we even take our training into offices and factories.\n\nStudents who study in Canterbury will get the opportunity to experience life in a 2000-year old English city. It is a vibrant and safe university city, close to London, in the beautiful ‘Garden of England’. This is a great opportunity to make friends from England and around the world, expand your world view and experience personal growth. As your ‘home away from home’, Warnborough College is committed to your success.', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
